<p>Hello!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password for the <i>FAQ Bot Framework</i>. You can do this through the link below:</p>

<p><%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token, host: Rails.application.secrets.domain_name, port: Rails.application.secrets.port) %></p>

